  "description": {
    "zh": "嘿，说真的，其实我对之前的结果差强人意，所以我们得一探再探。\n\n也许我们需要用这把枪对付一些更高级别的目标？比如其他PMC之类的？也许行得通说不定！你搞得定吗？别忘了把他们的狗牌带回来给我。\n\n随便BEAR，USEC都行，是个狗牌就OK。",
    "en": "Hey, I'm not really satisfied with the results if I'm honest, so we're taking it a step up.\n\nMaybe we need to use this gun against higher-priority targets? Maybe other operators, yes that would work! Can you handle that? And don't forget to bring me their dogtags.\n\nIt won't matter if you take out BEAR or USEC operators."
  },
